  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. This package declares assuranceLevel Medium and records an Accepted decision; however, multiple credibility factors have achievedLevel below requiredLevel, constituting a Critical W-AR-02 weakener that makes the declared assurance level unsupportable (COMPOUND-03).",
  "assuranceLevel": "Medium",
  "couName": "VAD use",
  "decision": "Accepted",
  "deviceClass": "Class III",
  "modelRiskLevel": 5,
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-absolute",
